## â“ What is Auto Scaling?
**Auto Scaling** automatically adjusts the number of EC2 instances based on system demand or predefined conditions.

> ðŸª Example: Imagine your app as a pizza shop. During lunch rush, orders spikeâ€”Auto Scaling adds more delivery drivers (EC2 instances). When itâ€™s quiet, it sends them home to save costs.

